<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Seinsheim zu Hohenkottenheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Ulrich Schlüsselfelder, Bürger zu Nürnberg, selbst antwortet.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_98" id="49r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_98_r1l24"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Sawnſheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒ </del> von kottenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_98_r1l26"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von vlrich Sluſſelfelders </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l27"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers wegen / Darümb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir Jn durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l28">beſant vnd cʒurede geſacʒt / vnd der hat vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / Er vvölle </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l29">euch ſelber ein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> an <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> brief / darümb <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_98_r1l33"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc </ab></add> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l30">in dıe <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Andree Anno xiiij<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_98" id="49r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Sawnsheim von Kottenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Ulrich Slusselfelders,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers, wegen, darümb
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in durch
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besant und czu rede gesaczt; und der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, er wölle euch selber ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> an <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        brief darümb <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                <add><expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc.</add>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                        Andree anno xiiii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
